net.sourceforge.JDash.ecu.param
Interface StringParameter

All Known Implementing Classes:
DTCMetaParam
public interface StringParameter

This interface is used by the JDAsh system to identify parameters that are string values, and NOT double values. The default is Double, but some parameters like DTC Codes are not represeneted as doubles.
